accountability must also sit locally.

57
00:02:25.625 --> 00:02:27.355
Otherwise, when performance is tested,

58
00:02:27.425 --> 00:02:28.715
ownership will be blurred.

59
00:02:29.695 --> 00:02:31.595
The bill strengthens the director general's powers

60
00:02:31.595 --> 00:02:33.795
to drive national consistency, and that is appropriate.

61
